<paragraph id="IFRS17_BC22" base="F55750940"><paranum>BC22</paranum><prolog><data name="standard_number" value="IFRS 17"/><data name="paranum" value="BC22"/></prolog><body><p id="IFRS17_P5815">After initial recognition, IFRS 17 requires the measurement of the fulfilment cash flows to reflect estimates based on current assumptions, for the reasons set out in <xref id="IFRS17_X1393" base="F59357612" href="IFRS17_BC20.dita#IFRS17_BC20">paragraphs BC20</xref> and <xref id="IFRS17_X1394" base="F59357613" href="IFRS17_gBC155-BC156.dita#IFRS17_gBC155-BC156/IFRS17_gBC155-BC156_TI">BC155</xref>.</p></body></paragraph>